<DOCNO> LA112690-0001 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 313431 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 26, 1990, Monday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
