poison was stored. ; Photo, Marjorie Grisak says she was made ill by poison. ; 
Photo, Marjorie Grisak holds a bag of deadly rodent bait. Grisak claims she was 
not properly trained to handle the poisonous substance. DAVE GATLEY / Los 
