Brad Friedel. It was the first time the Mustangs had been shut out this season. 
</P>
<P>
The second-ranked Bruins advance to play fourth-ranked North Carolina State on 
Saturday at the University of South Florida in Tampa. The other semifinal pits 
top-ranked Evansville versus fourth-ranked Rutgers. The Division I championship 
game is Sunday. IAN JAQUISS 
