hits Bear quarterback Jim Harbaugh, causing him to fumble. Reuters; Photo, Carl 
Lee of the Vikings (left) pressures Ron Morris of the Bears into dropping a 
pass during the Vikings' impressive 41-13 victory. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
