RACIAL RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; GOVERNMENT REFORM; APARTHEID; SOUTH AFRICA -- 
ECONOMY; AFRICA -- ECONOMY; ECONOMIC SANCTIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
