TOUGH INDUSTRY: The banking business has been a real eye-opener for Richard 
Stenton, chairman of Laguna Bank in Laguna Beach. Stenton has gone through 
three presidents at his bank and now may sell it. . . . "When I got in this 
industry, I thought everybody paid off their loans," he said. But tough times 
