surround Cox's fourth-quarter fumble. Green recovered. LENNY IGNELZI / 
Associated Press; Photo, Seattle's Donald Miller (99) and Robert Blackmon (25) 
chase loose ball on a two-fumble punt return. DAVID McNEW / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
