<P>
Column; Corporate Earnings 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BROAD INC; BROKERAGE FIRMS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112690-0107 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 313761 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 26, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
